            "text_mgb_mobile": 10
          }
        },
        "custom_text_HxPGTr": {
          "type": "custom_text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Confidence in a bikini is rarely about one single detail. It comes from a combination of fit, cut, fabric, support, and how the bikini feels once you are actually wearing it in real life. When these elements work together, a bikini stops feeling like something you are managing and starts feeling like something you can simply wear.\n<br><br>\nTaking the time to consider how different styles make you feel allows you to choose swimwear more intuitively. Instead of focusing on trends or assumptions, confidence comes from understanding what feels comfortable, secure, and aligned with how you want to move through the day. When a bikini supports the body and feels considered in its design, confidence follows naturally.\n<br><br>\nFor those who prefer a more cohesive look, exploring <a href=\"/collections/bikini-sets\" title=\"Bikini sets\">bikini sets</a> can make choosing easier. Coordinated tops and bottoms are designed to work together in terms of fit, proportion, and support, helping remove uncertainty and allowing you to focus on how the swimwear feels rather than how it is styled.\n<br><br>\nUltimately, the right bikini is the one that allows you to feel at ease. When you trust the fit and construction, confidence becomes effortless, and that is what makes a bikini truly work.",
            "remove_br_tag": false,
            "tag": "p",
            "fontf": "inherit",
            "text_cl": "#000000",
            "text_fs": 16,
            "text_lh": 24,
            "text_fw": 300,
            "text_ls": 0,
            "font_italic": false,
